ed="T" n="0833b19"/><persName key="A012427">釋和和</persName>者，莫詳氏族、本生。其為僧也狂而<lb
ed="T" n="0833b20"/>不亂，愚而有知，罔測其由<ptr target="#n2521"/>。發言多中，時<lb
ed="T" n="0833b21"/>號為聖。<placeName key="PL000000042147">安國寺</placeName><ptr target="#n558"/>中居住，出入無拘撿。見<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042147">本<lb
ed="T" n="0833b22"/>寺</ref>修營殿閣未就──有<persName key="A019444"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>越</sic><corr>代</corr></choice>國公主</persName><ptr target="#n2522"/>降<persName key="A012428"><persName><anchor xml:id="beg0833004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>榮</sic><corr>滎</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0833004"/>陽</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0833b23"/><persName>鄭萬鈞</persName></persName>，雖琴瑟相諧，而數年無子<ptr target="#n2523"/>──<persName key="A012427">和</persName>因<ptr target="#n2524"/>至<lb
ed="T" n="0833b24"/><ref type="person" target="#A019444">公主</ref>家，<persName key="A012428">鈞</persName>焚香灑掃以待之。<ref type="person" target="#A019444">主</ref>拜跪歸向<ptr target="#n2525"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0833b25"/><persName key="A012428">鈞</persName>祈告之曰：「某自叨選尚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1712"/>，願得一子為<lb
ed="T" n="0833b26"/>嗣，唯<ref type="person" target="#A012427">師</ref>能致之乎？」<persName key="A012427">和</persName>曰：「易耳！但遺<ref type="person" target="#A012427">我</ref>三千<lb
ed="T" n="0833b27"/>疋絹，<ref type="person" target="#A019444">主</ref>當誕二男。」<persName key="A012428">鈞</persName>勤重<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g250"/>如聽<name>佛</name>語，出絹<lb
ed="T" n="0833b28"/>如所求施之。<persName key="A012427">和</persName>取付修寺殿閣功德主。乃<lb
ed="T" n="0833b29"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A019444">主</ref>有娠矣，<ref type="person" target="#A012427">吾</ref>令二天人下為<ref type="person" target="#A019444">公主</ref>作兒。<pb ed="T" n="0833c" xml:id="T50.2061.0833c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0833c01"/>所憂者<ref type="person" target="#A019444">公主</ref>不能併妊二子乎？為㝈乳包<lb
ed="T" n="0833c02"/>羞耳<ptr target="#n2526"/>。<ref type="person" target="#A012427">吾</ref>俾其同年而前後誕之。」果如其言，<lb
ed="T" n="0833c03"/>歲初年末，各生之矣。長曰<persName key="A012429">潛耀</persName>，次曰<persName key="A012430">晦明</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0833c04"/>皆美丈夫，後博涉成事焉<ptr target="#n2527"/>。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>之間傳<anchor xml:id="beg0833sgsz11"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0833sgsz11"/>沸<lb
ed="T" n="0833c05"/>渭<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1713"/>，量其位地，不可輕議哉。</p>
